Determines whether to perform monitoring on DB Connection and SQL.
When this option is set to false, all DB and SQL settings are disabled.

---

* Default value: true
* Type: Boolean
* Restart: Not required
* Related options
    * [enable_connection_leak_trace](./agentHelp?key=enable_connection_leak_trace&type=2)
    * [sql_fetch_warning_count](./agentHelp?key=sql_fetch_warning_count&type=2)
    * [enable_sql_exception_event](./agentHelp?key=enable_sql_exception_event&type=2)
* Supported version: 5.2.2.1